## Expected Outcomes

By executing across these paths over 90 days, KSPF should:
- Have a clear, differentiated positioning that doesn't compete on price
- Have a consistently active pipeline (10–15 warm leads at all times)
- Have a published portfolio that converts inbound interest
- Have a pricing structure that reflects actual value delivered
- Have the studio OS and AI tools working together (brand voice → RAG → AI-assisted drafting)
- Have a clearer picture of whether to stay solo or bring in an Integrator

